column2: select   A.specObjID,   A.subclass,   A.plateid,   A.mjd,   A.fiberid,   A.subclass,   A.spectrotype,   B.h_beta_flux,   B.h_alpha_flux,   B.nii_#_flux,   B.h_beta_flux_err,   B.h_alpha_flux_err,   B.nii_#_flux_err      INTO MYDB.Rosi_muestra2 FROM   galSpecInfo as A    JOIN galSpecLine as B on A.specObjID = B.specObjID where      A.spectrotype = &&& and     # > A.z and     h_alpha_flux > # and     B.nii_#_flux/h_alpha_flux > #
